      <title>哥伦比亚财政部长表示燃料补贴是一个主要问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/colombia-s-finance-chief-says-fuel-subsidies-are-a-major-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚最高财政官员表示，削减高额燃料补贴成本比与国际货币基金组织重新谈判协议更为紧迫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/colombia-s-finance-chief-says-fuel-subsidies-are-a-major-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>除非马杜罗迅速采取行动，否则美国将重新实施委内瑞拉石油禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果尼古拉斯·马杜罗政权在未来两天内不采取措施履行一项协议，允许在定于 7 月举行的选举中进行更公平的投票，总统乔·拜登政府打算重新对委内瑞拉实施石油制裁，结束六个月的缓刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/us-to-reimpose-venezuela-oil-ban-unless-maduro-acts-quickly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉将把扣押的康菲石油资产交给鲜为人知的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/venezuela-to-hand-seized-conoco-oil-assets-to-little-known-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉计划利用一家鲜为人知的公司来接管曾经由康菲石油公司运营的关键油田和设施，因为该国在美国决定是否恢复制裁的最后期限之前迅速签署协议，这将为参与者关闭大门希望进入南美国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/venezuela-to-hand-seized-conoco-oil-assets-to-little-known-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷顶级首席执行官在 Patagonia Retreat 盛赞 Milei</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/top-argentina-ceos-to-heap-praise-on-javier-milei-at-patagonia-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于三位数的通货膨胀抑制了消费者支出，爱德华多·埃尔斯斯坦 (Eduardo Elsztain) 正准备迎接他的购物中心销售受到影响。然而哈维尔·米雷就任总统四个月后，这位房地产大亨比以往任何时候都更加看好阿根廷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/top-argentina-ceos-to-heap-praise-on-javier-milei-at-patagonia-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称中美债务给全球公共财政带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/imf-says-us-china-debt-pose-risks-for-global-public-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织(IMF)官员表示，世界两大经济竞争对手中国和美国将在未来五年内推动全球公共债务的增长，而美国的支出通过维持高利率给许多其他国家带来麻烦。在一份报告中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/imf-says-us-china-debt-pose-risks-for-global-public-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
